rows.label: qev300121_MSG0001
rows.name:
It's quite the honor to have you accept one of our
requests.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev300121_MSG0002
rows.name: You're here to deliver the miranium, I trust?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev300121_SEL0021
rows.name: Hold on to your miranium for now.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev300121_MSG0004
rows.name:
You have my thanks. I'll be sure to put in a good word
to the CEO for you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev300121_MSG0005
rows.name:
Heh, leave it to a top BLADE.
You really know how to make a guy sweat![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev300121_MSG0006
rows.name:
I'm stunned someone of your caliber doesn't actually
have the 2,400 units of miranium on hand.
Hurry back once you do![ST:wait ]
